---
title: Asian Sweet Chilli-Glazed Pork Tacos with Pear & Creamy Slaw
description: Saucy pork mince is seriously good in tacos – it fills them up nicely and makes delicious mouthfuls of juicy flavour. Add a creamy slaw, crisp cucumber and a sweet chilli glaze and prepare to be rapt, in more ways than one!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/asian-pork-meatball-tacos-6673caaf.jpg
